page.title: 09DORKING OPEN AIR MARKET
page.content: Stalls Information __________________ The 12th July 1985 was a sunny day for our survey. There were 41 store holders at the market,providing a wide variety of goods,being offered for sale including: Wickerwork,Bags,Meats, Ladies Clothes-3,Cusions,Freezer Lorry, Men's clothes,D.I.Y.,Nightwear, Pictures,Underwear,Bric-a-Brac, Towels,Records+tapes,Fabrics-2, Religious,Jewellery-2,Toys, Haberdashery,Sweets,Plants+Flowers-3, Fish,Wool,Cheese and Buiscuits, Shoes,Wholefoods,Electronics, Eggs-2,Swimming costumes,Ice-cream, Repair parts,Fruit and vegetables.
